-- MOVES-Mizuho Securities names DeSalvo as equity division head
-- 
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 12:59PM EDT
-- None



Sept 16 (Reuters) - Mizuho Securities USA, a unit of Mizuho Financial Group Inc <8411.T>, appointed Matthew DeSalvo as executive managing director and head of its equity division.

He will report to Chief Executive John Koudounis.